<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Quick-Pay</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 10px;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 95%;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid gray;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #3B82F6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #3B82F6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #2563EB;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        /* Media Queries for Responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .content p {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .btn {
                padding: 8px 20px;
                font-size: 12px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .content p {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .btn {
                padding: 6px 18px;
                font-size: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Quick-Pay, <%= username %>!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>We are thrilled to have you on board. Quick-Pay offers a wide range of services to make your life easier
                and more convenient.</p>
            <p>We are committed to providing you with the best service experience. If you have any questions or need
                assistance, please feel free to contact our support team.</p>
            <a href="https://quick-pay-liard.vercel.app/" class="btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards, <br /> The Quick-Pay Team</p>
            <p>If you no longer wish to receive these emails, you can <a href="<%= unsubscribe_link %>"
                    style="color: #3B82F6;">unsubscribe here</a>.</p>
            <p>Â© 2024 Quick-Pay.finance All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
